OL,6,FA man from has been jailed for making
OL,7,Fand supplying improvised firearms in
OL,8,Fthe city and in London.
OL,10,FKemarn Riley who's 24 and from Ward
OL,11,FEnd, was sentenced to twelve years and
OL,12,Fnine months for the manufacture of a
OL,13,Fweapon and ammunition, at on the 2nd
OL,14,FMay.
OL,16,FRiley also received five years each
OL,17,Ffor two counts of possession of a
OL,18,Ffirearm - his sentences will run
OL,19,Fconcurrently.
