OL,6,FPolice began investigating him in
OL,7,FJanuary 2023. Officers attended an
OL,8,Faddress in Headingley Road in , in
OL,9,Fconnection with an earlier report of
OL,10,Fcriminal damage.
OL,12,FThey found a handgun, later identified
OL,13,Fas a converted blank firing pistol,
OL,14,Fhidden behind a shoulder bag in the
OL,15,Fback garden.
OL,17,FThe bag contained two live shotgun
OL,18,Fshells. Another bag had two metal
OL,19,Fpipes, which officers suspected could
OL,20,Fmake an improvised weapon commonly
OL,21,Freferred to as a "slam gun'".
