OL,6,FThe weapons, ammunition and bags were
OL,7,Fseized from the property for analysis
OL,8,Fand were forensically linked to Riley,
OL,9,Ffollowing testing.
OL,11,FIn February, another slam gun was
OL,12,Ffound in a vehicle in Handsworth.
OL,13,FAfter analysis, it was again traced
OL,14,Fback to Riley.
OL,16,FHe was arrested at his new home
OL,17,Faddress on Asquith Road in Ward End on
OL,18,Fthe 28th February. He'd moved there
OL,19,Fshortly after weapons and ammunition
OL,20,Fwere found at his previous residence
OL,21,Fon Headingley Road.
