OL,6,FAt his new home police found a bag
OL,7,Fwith imitation firearms, shotgun
OL,8,Fcartridges and metal pipes, similar to
OL,9,Fthe ones discovered earlier used to
OL,10,Fmake slam guns.
OL,12,FAn examination of Riley's seized phone
OL,13,Funcovered messages, images and
OL,14,Fsearches that suggested he was
OL,15,Finvolved in the sale of firearms.
OL,17,FDuring custody questioning, Riley
OL,18,Fadmitted to buying pipes for an
OL,19,Fassociate but claimed to have no
OL,20,Fknowledge of their intended use.
