OL,6,F"These weapons can maim and kill"
OL,8,FIn March 2023, Metropolitan Police
OL,9,Fofficers got in touch with about
OL,10,Ffirearms they had seized in London,
OL,11,Faround the same time the discoveries
OL,12,Fwere made in Birmingham.
OL,14,FThe slam guns were of a similar
OL,15,Fdescription and were also forensically
OL,16,Flinked to Riley.
