OL,6,FHe continued to offer no comment
OL,7,Faround the sale of weapons, and
OL,8,Fpleaded guilty to the possession
OL,9,Fcharges relating to the weapons seized
OL,10,Fin Birmingham in January 2023.
OL,12,FPC Owen Zambra, Investigations Officer
OL,13,Ffrom the West Midlands Police Major
OL,14,FCrime Unit said:
OL,16,F"We built a strong case against Kemarn
OL,17,FRiley and are pleased with this
OL,18,Fresult. The message is clear that we
OL,19,Fwon't tolerate anyone profiting from
OL,20,Fthe production and supply of illegal
OL,21,Ffirearms.
